<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Refund Policy - LegalPracticeAI</title>
    <%- include('partials/seo-head', {
        title: 'Refund Policy - LegalPracticeAI',
        description: 'LegalPracticeAI Refund Policy - Learn about our 30-day money-back guarantee and cancellation policy.',
        canonical: 'https://legalpracticeai.com/refund-policy'
    }) %>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/custom.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main class="py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-lg-10">
                    <nav aria-label="breadcrumb" class="mb-4">
                        <ol class="breadcrumb">
                            <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                            <li class="breadcrumb-item active">Refund Policy</li>
                        </ol>
                    </nav>

                    <h1 class="mb-4">Refund Policy</h1>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-4">Last Updated: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' }) %></p>

                    <div class="alert alert-success mb-4">
                        <h5 class="alert-heading"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt me-2"></i>30-Day Money-Back Guarantee</h5>
                        <p class="mb-0">We offer a full refund within 30 days of purchase if you're not satisfied with our service.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h2 class="h4">1. Refund Eligibility</h2>
                            <p>You may request a refund if:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Your request is made within 30 days of your initial purchase</li>
                                <li>You are on a paid subscription plan (Professional or Enterprise)</li>
                                <li>You have not previously received a refund for LegalPracticeAI services</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h2 class="h4">2. How to Request a Refund</h2>
                            <p>To request a refund:</p>
                            <ol>
                                <li>Email us at <strong>support@legalpracticeai.com</strong> with subject "Refund Request"</li>
                                <li>Include your account email and reason for the refund</li>
                                <li>We will process your request within 5-7 business days</li>
                            </ol>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h2 class="h4">3. Refund Processing</h2>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Refunds are processed to the original payment method</li>
                                <li>Credit card refunds may take 5-10 business days to appear</li>
                                <li>PayPal refunds are typically processed within 24-48 hours</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h2 class="h4">4. Subscription Cancellation</h2>
                            <p>You can cancel your subscription at any time:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Your access continues until the end of your billing period</li>
                                <li>No partial refunds for unused portions of the billing period</li>
                                <li>Previously generated documents remain accessible</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h2 class="h4">5. Non-Refundable Items</h2>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Free plan usage</li>
                                <li>API usage charges beyond included limits</li>
                                <li>Custom enterprise implementations</li>
                                <li>Third-party integration fees</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h2 class="h4">6. Contact Us</h2>
                            <p>For refund inquiries:</p>
                            <p><strong>Email:</strong> support@legalpracticeai.com<br>
                            <strong>Response Time:</strong> Within 24 hours</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
